Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Asyut, 15 Feb (MENA)--The Asyut security authorities 
this evening arrested a fugitive terrorist charged with many 
crimes during a security raid on his home in al-Walidiyah in 
Asyut Governorate. 
  The terrorist, 'Atif 'Ali Farghali, who was regarded as one 
of the dangerous elements in Asyut, was hit by two bullets in 
the abdomen and shoulder. He was taken to the hospital under 
heavy guard and remanded into custody. The prosecution's second 
branch in Asyut has been instructed to start an investigation. 
[passage omitted on non-terrorism arrests] 

